\is1 Introduction
\ip Si Titu, kene sikandin Hudiyu and kene egpalintutuu dengan of God. Piru hengkayi of mewuri e timpu na-Kristuwanen e sikandin. Ne puun dutu, neyimu sikandin talagbulig of Paul of me work rin. This sulat, impeuyan of Paul there to kandin of inggaat din there to Krita eyew eg-uyan of punduk of believers. (The Krita, pulu of dahat sakup of Grisya.)
\ip Ne due tatelu impanengneng of this sulat: The first, impasuman-suman si Titu ke nekey the eleg egbatasanen of me pangulu of believers. Keilangan egpakataha sikandin here tenged su masulug the mareet batasan of matig-Krita and due masulug talagpanulu kene true/correct egpasuwey of believers.
\ip The second, intambahan si Titu ke egmenuwen din of teaching the nalein-lein people there to punduk of believers, lagkes seeye se me lukes-lukes and me uripen, and seeye se bayew e me buyag me lukes and women. (Ne iyan egpanulu of me mengebay the buyag e women.)
\ip Te ending, migtambahan of Paul si Titu concerning the Kristuwanen peg-ugpe, and pegpanalliya of peg-ehet of duma, pegpaapuley, and pegbaad-part there to punduk of believers. Impasuman-suman again of Paul si Titu egpakatuman ki of seeye se insuhu kanta tenged of kaluwasan imbehey kanta of Hisu Kristu.
\ip Egkeupian si Paul egkanengnengan here of this sulat amana impurtanti there to believers the peggimu of meupiya (1:6; 2:7,14; 3:1,8-9,14) piru kene sika egpakaluwas (3:5).
